  "text": "Theorem 2.1 (Lemmas 2-4 in [CITATION_1] ). Let L be a Lie algebra, let V be a vector space with fixed basis {e 1 , . . . , e s } over a field F, and let ϑ, η be elements of Z 2 (L, V ). ",
